sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Gateway / Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant HTTPRoute as HTTPRoute / VirtualService
    participant EPP as EPP Scheduler<br/>(ExtProc gRPC)
    participant Svc as K8s Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Agent as kserve-agent<br/>9081/TCP HTTP
    participant Model as Model Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant StorageInit as storage-initializer<br/>(init container)
    participant Storage as Remote Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure/HF)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMCtrl as localmodel-controller
    participant LMAgent as localmodelnode-agent
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NodePV as Node-Local PV

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,Model: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (InferenceService - Raw Deployment)
        Client->>GW: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        GW->>HTTPRoute: Route matching
        HTTPRoute->>Svc: Forward to Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP (cluster internal)
        Svc->>Agent: Forward to agent sidecar<br/>9081/TCP HTTP
        Agent->>Model: Proxy to model container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        Model-->>Agent: Prediction result (JSON)
        Agent-->>Svc: Response
        Svc-->>GW: Response
        GW-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>200 OK
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over StorageInit,Storage: Flow 2: Model Download (Storage Initializer)
        Note right of StorageInit: Runs as init container<br/>before model server starts
        StorageInit->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Cloud credentials (IAM/Key/Token)
        Storage-->>StorageInit: Model artifacts
        StorageInit->>StorageInit: Write to model volume mount<br/>(filesystem)
        Note right of StorageInit: Model server starts<br/>after init completes
    end

    rect rgb(245, 230, 255)
        Note over Client,EPP: Flow 3: LLM Inference with EPP Scheduler
        Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        GW->>EPP: ExtProc filter (gRPC)<br/>mTLS (Istio)
        EPP->>EPP: Select optimal pod<br/>(KV cache util, queue depth)
        EPP-->>GW: Selected backend endpoint
        GW->>Model: Forward to selected pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (mesh)
        Model-->>GW: Streaming response
        GW-->>Client: SSE / JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over LMCtrl,NodePV: Flow 4: Local Model Caching
        LMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch LocalModelCache CRs<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        LMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create PV/PVC<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
        K8sAPI-->>LMCtrl: PV/PVC created
        LMAgent->>K8sAPI: Watch LocalModelNode CRs<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        LMAgent->>K8sAPI: Create download Job<br/>(uses storage-initializer image)
        Note right of LMAgent: Download Job runs on node
        K8sAPI->>Storage: Job: Download model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Cloud credentials
        Storage-->>K8sAPI: Model artifacts
        K8sAPI->>NodePV: Write to node-local PV<br/>(filesystem, SHA-256 dedup)
    end
